OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister to intervene over 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcouncil teacher cuts       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's education secretary         
OL,6, Shirley-Anne Somerville is preparing to
OL,7, intervene to stop local councils       
OL,8, cutting teacher numbers.               
OL,10,FThe BBC understands that Ms Somerville 
OL,11,Fis considering options and is likely to
OL,12,Fannounce action within days.           
OL,14,FShe is also expected to prevent the    
OL,15,Fnumber of school hours being reduced.  
OL,17,FIt follows reports that several local  
OL,18,Fauthorities, including SNP-led Glasgow 
OL,19,Fcity council, are considering education
OL,20,Fcuts to balance their budgets.         
